{"componentChunkName":"component---src-pages-diaries-markdown-remark-frontmatter-slug-jsx","path":"/diaries/kashgar-hostal/","result":{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"html":"<p>因为前天发生的住宿问题，导致昨晚在塔县换到了一个还不错的酒店，可惜没有好好感受独享的酒店标间，给老妹当之心大姐当到晚上三点。顺带一提，这家酒店的前台塔吉克族小哥长得有点像内马尔……</p>\n<p>相比前两天，今天的旅行格外轻松，从塔县出发几十公里就能到达塔合曼湿地，类似昨天的金草滩，但是因为距离慕士塔格峰更近，而且是在城外，所以在显得也更加苍茫，壮阔。</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 650px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/0c9be11f7bd9de90c35ca5bfab7a0c93/9281d/2023-10-04-taheman-wetland-park.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 56.44171779141104%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"wetland park\"\n        title=\"\"\n        src=\"/static/0c9be11f7bd9de90c35ca5bfab7a0c93/6aca1/2023-10-04-taheman-wetland-park.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/0c9be11f7bd9de90c35ca5bfab7a0c93/d2f63/2023-10-04-taheman-wetland-park.jpg 163w,\n/static/0c9be11f7bd9de90c35ca5bfab7a0c93/c989d/2023-10-04-taheman-wetland-park.jpg 325w,\n/static/0c9be11f7bd9de90c35ca5bfab7a0c93/6aca1/2023-10-04-taheman-wetland-park.jpg 650w,\n/static/0c9be11f7bd9de90c35ca5bfab7a0c93/7c09c/2023-10-04-taheman-wetland-park.jpg 975w,\n/static/0c9be11f7bd9de90c35ca5bfab7a0c93/01ab0/2023-10-04-taheman-wetland-park.jpg 1300w,\n/static/0c9be11f7bd9de90c35ca5bfab7a0c93/9281d/2023-10-04-taheman-wetland-park.jpg 2365w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 650px) 100vw, 650px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n        decoding=\"async\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>从塔合曼湿地出发前行近百公里，就到达了喀拉库勒湖，下车时湖水在阳光下倒映着远处的慕士塔格峰。沿着湖边，走到一处宽阔处，两位柯尔克孜族马童走来问我是否要骑白马，对不起，我背叛了阶级兄弟，还是骑了。现世报来的很快，刚出发了百来米，远处的乌云就已经压到近前，大雪扑面而来。</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 650px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/d524c46f2f3aef9131bfa5a962c22732/9281d/2023-10-04-karakul-lake.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 56.44171779141104%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"karakul lake\"\n        title=\"\"\n        src=\"/static/d524c46f2f3aef9131bfa5a962c22732/6aca1/2023-10-04-karakul-lake.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/d524c46f2f3aef9131bfa5a962c22732/d2f63/2023-10-04-karakul-lake.jpg 163w,\n/static/d524c46f2f3aef9131bfa5a962c22732/c989d/2023-10-04-karakul-lake.jpg 325w,\n/static/d524c46f2f3aef9131bfa5a962c22732/6aca1/2023-10-04-karakul-lake.jpg 650w,\n/static/d524c46f2f3aef9131bfa5a962c22732/7c09c/2023-10-04-karakul-lake.jpg 975w,\n/static/d524c46f2f3aef9131bfa5a962c22732/01ab0/2023-10-04-karakul-lake.jpg 1300w,\n/static/d524c46f2f3aef9131bfa5a962c22732/9281d/2023-10-04-karakul-lake.jpg 2365w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 650px) 100vw, 650px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n        decoding=\"async\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>在漫天风雪里，看着山远去～我被冻得无法自已！</p>\n<p>从喀湖出发继续北行返程，沿途经过一处被风雨严重侵蚀的红山峡谷，当地司机向导称之为“气泡峡谷”，因其山体被风蚀的千疮百孔而得名。峡谷间散落的的碎石被风化的严重到了稍微使劲一摔即可将之一分为二，同行女生说这里特别像魔鬼城，因为没去过魔鬼城，所以对此不置可否，但是景色确实称得上是一奇。</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 650px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/a8f893d4af77fe11168d621cf2cd92f8/e1596/2023-10-04-bubble-gorge.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 74.84662576687117%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"bubble gorge\"\n        title=\"\"\n        src=\"/static/a8f893d4af77fe11168d621cf2cd92f8/6aca1/2023-10-04-bubble-gorge.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/a8f893d4af77fe11168d621cf2cd92f8/d2f63/2023-10-04-bubble-gorge.jpg 163w,\n/static/a8f893d4af77fe11168d621cf2cd92f8/c989d/2023-10-04-bubble-gorge.jpg 325w,\n/static/a8f893d4af77fe11168d621cf2cd92f8/6aca1/2023-10-04-bubble-gorge.jpg 650w,\n/static/a8f893d4af77fe11168d621cf2cd92f8/7c09c/2023-10-04-bubble-gorge.jpg 975w,\n/static/a8f893d4af77fe11168d621cf2cd92f8/01ab0/2023-10-04-bubble-gorge.jpg 1300w,\n/static/a8f893d4af77fe11168d621cf2cd92f8/e1596/2023-10-04-bubble-gorge.jpg 2048w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 650px) 100vw, 650px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n        decoding=\"async\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>回到喀什就到了分别的时刻，加了司机大哥的微信，说来惭愧，至此才知道他姓何。来到青旅，事情反而开始向着预料之外发展了。登记的时候发现还有一个外国人，而且还和我分到了一个房间。他开局就自我介绍自己来自日本，我一听就来劲了，活着的在眼前的日本人可不常见啊。和他聊天之后才发现他还是一个有共产主义倾向的大四学生，为了写毕业论文而来到中国，此前已经走访了中亚五斯坦，甚至在那里收集了戈尔巴乔夫时代的苏联勋章。和他聊至兴起，还即兴来了一首“牢不可破的联盟”，着实让我大为震惊，就差杀鸡开坛拜把子了。</p>\n<p>Interesting!</p>\n<p>因为同住的人中英语都不太行，所以就由我来作为他的导游兼翻译，带他游览了喀什古城，高台民居，最后又吃了当地特色的丁丁炒面。小日子过得不错的户田雄毅同学当即表示“第一次吃到层次这么鲜明，口感这么丰富的食物”，甚至表示要把我的半盘都拿走吃掉，没错，我们的户田同学自己点的是盖饭，我点的是丁丁炒面，本来是想让他品尝一下分了他一勺，结果孩子看我不饿当即表示“交给我吧”。这种有趣的情景我也是第一次见到，当然是不能错过啦。当然作为中日两个左翼年轻人，交流的话题肯定少不了对当前两国政府行为的讨论，他鲜明的表示非常讨厌日本政府将核污染水排入大海的决定。我也和他分享了我对当前国内政治和局势的看法和观点。虽然存在分歧，但是至少可以求同存异，最起码，他是能够在毛主席像前大大方方唱出义勇军进行曲的人。</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 650px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/162b314e90583ffeda53ebac07bcfb8b/e1596/2023-10-04-japanese-friend.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 74.84662576687117%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"japanese friend\"\n        title=\"\"\n        src=\"/static/162b314e90583ffeda53ebac07bcfb8b/6aca1/2023-10-04-japanese-friend.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/162b314e90583ffeda53ebac07bcfb8b/d2f63/2023-10-04-japanese-friend.jpg 163w,\n/static/162b314e90583ffeda53ebac07bcfb8b/c989d/2023-10-04-japanese-friend.jpg 325w,\n/static/162b314e90583ffeda53ebac07bcfb8b/6aca1/2023-10-04-japanese-friend.jpg 650w,\n/static/162b314e90583ffeda53ebac07bcfb8b/7c09c/2023-10-04-japanese-friend.jpg 975w,\n/static/162b314e90583ffeda53ebac07bcfb8b/01ab0/2023-10-04-japanese-friend.jpg 1300w,\n/static/162b314e90583ffeda53ebac07bcfb8b/e1596/2023-10-04-japanese-friend.jpg 2048w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 650px) 100vw, 650px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n        decoding=\"async\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>“喀什，有意思的是人”，这句话我好像小有体会了。</p>\n<p>因为今天和新认识的国际友人交谈甚欢，结果导致我的皮带又没买成，将就着到莎车再买吧。</p>\n<p>明天，出发，莎车！</p>","frontmatter":{"date":"October 04, 2023","slug":"/kashgar-hostal","title":"喀什青旅"}}},"pageContext":{"id":"c863858a-b921-55c1-a622-d24f23492909","frontmatter__slug":"/kashgar-hostal","__params":{"frontmatter__slug":"kashgar-hostal"}}},"staticQueryHashes":[],"slicesMap":{}}